## вљ™пёЏ Setup Instructions

### рџ”№ 1. Clone the repository

```
git clone <https://github.com/sugandha-a/finance-dashboard>
cd finance-dashboard-backend
```

### рџ”№ 2. Install dependencies

Backend:

```
npm install
```

Frontend:

```
cd finance-frontend
npm install
```

---

### рџ”№ 3. Configure Environment Variables

Create `.env` file in backend:

```
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
```

---

### рџ”№ 4. Run the application

Backend:

```
npm run dev
```

Frontend:

```
npm start
```

## рџ”— API Endpoints

### рџ”ђ Auth

* POST `/api/users/register`
* POST `/api/users/login`

### рџ‘¤ Users (Admin)

* GET `/api/users`
* PUT `/api/users/:id/role`
* PUT `/api/users/:id/status`

### рџ’° Records

* POST `/api/records`
* GET `/api/records`
* PUT `/api/records/:id`
* DELETE `/api/records/:id`

### рџ“Љ Dashboard

* GET `/api/dashboard`

